      ** Transaction information in a single large field from source system
      *
     C                   PARM                    NSRMParm
      *
     C                   PARM                    FldNameArr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDArr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaArr
     C                   PARM                    WFldNamArr
     C                   PARM                    WMsgIDArr
     C                   PARM                    WMsgDtaArr
     C                   PARM                    MsgFArray
     C                   PARM                    Buffer
      *
     C                   ENDIF
